Packages
jyzer The main-package of the JYzer.
jyzer.gui This package contains the GUI components & other classes that are used by and only by the GUI components.
jyzer.gui.guihelpers This package classes that are used by and only by the GUI components, like file filters, table models, and so on.
jyzer.items This package contains the main contents (at an abstract level) of a classfile, such as methods, fields, interfaces, and so on.
jyzer.items.accessflags This package contains the main classes used for accessflag processing.
jyzer.items.attributes This package contains the main classes used for attribute processing.
jyzer.items.attributes.types This package contains all of the recent known attributes.
jyzer.items.constantpool This package contains the main classes used for constant pool processing.
jyzer.items.constantpool.types This package contains all of the recent known constant pool entries.
jyzer.items.exceptions Package of the most common processing exceptions.
jyzer.items.factories Contains factories that helps building up the classfile.
jyzer.items.fields This package contains the main classes used for field processing.
jyzer.items.methods This package contains the main classes used for method processing.
